    <abstract>
      <t>The SR policy architecture defines the Prefix-SID algorithm, with an algorithm identifier included in the Prefix-SID advertisement. However, the Prefix-SID algorithm does not address scenarios where multiple algorithms share the same link resources. This document proposes adding the algorithm identifier in an Adjacency-SID advertisement.</t>
